title: T-shirt trends: 8 best-selling designs trend in 2023

content.content: In the ever-evolving world of fashion, t-shirt designs have become a canvas for self-expression and creativity. As we navigate through 2023, we're seeing an exciting blend of nostalgia, artistry, and innovation in t-shirt trends. From the resurgence of psychedelic and punk elements to the rise of hand-sketched and minimalist aesthetics, there's a design for every taste and style.
1. Psychedelic T-Shirts

Psychedelic prints are holographic designs with curving shapes and bold colors that have become exceedingly popular in the past few years. Psychedelic prints with futuristic concepts bring a mixture of fantasy and reality to the designs.

Most fans of psychedelic and dreamscape themes prefer these prints for parties and gatherings. The psychedelic bands logos are also luminescent and contribute to a wide variety of designs. As it becomes popular, more and more people are adopting the prints.
2. Famous Quotes and Sayings

A lot of people want their t-shirts to say things boldly and clearly. Being able to stand for something without saying a word is the bold choice that customers are willing to make. Especially after living in a world where keeping distance has become necessary and conversations have become limited.

If your apparel is advocating for a cause, be it social, political, environmental, etc., this category will sell itself. Plus, it gives you a huge variety of ideas. You can categorize these quotes and sayings into various subcategories and increase your offerings.
3. Doodle Artwork
Doodle artwork adds more playfulness to peoples lives and in their wardrobe. You can offer doodle designs that are very easy to implement.

You can make the designs in thin lines, wavy lines, different colors, and sizes, etc. Doodle artwork comes straight out of imagination. Whatever you imagine, you can implement in the designs. Start imagining and print it on the merch!
Conclusion

So, this was all about the latest t-shirt design trends and ideas. As the screen-printing technology is advancing, we see more and more evident changes. We believe that it will continue to be the best print method to grow your business with custom products for ages. We believe that the above-mentioned t-shirt design trends are going to soar to new heights.

title: Streetwear style-break boredom, reveal your own quality

content.content: In recent years, Streetwear fashion style has become increasingly explosive. Although it appeared about 40 years ago, Streetwear is still especially popular with modern youth thanks to its comfort, dynamism and unique impression. What has helped this fashion style become such a sought-after trend? Let's find out with Teeworld now?
1. The process of becoming a "king" of street fashion

When mentioning streetwear, we immediately think of Shawn Stussy - a designer from the California coast. In 1980, the Stssy brand logo first appeared on surfboards and t-shirts in small quantities. Possessing a comfortable fit and unique logo design has helped Stssy products make a big mark and are quickly sought after by the surfing and skateboarding community in the area.

The time that marked the "explosion" of streetwear style was in the 90s. At this time, streetwear received great acceptance from the skateboarder and Hip-hop followers community in New York. In 1994, Supreme's first store in Manhattan quickly attracted a lot of attention with its "drop" event. Every week this brand launches new designs in limited quantities.

In the early days of its appearance, streetwear did not receive high praise in the mainstream fashion industry. However, thanks to the strong influence of Hip-hop artists such as Kanye West, Nelly,... streetwear has become very popular.

In addition, collaborations between Supreme x Louis Vuitton 2017, Dior x KAWS 2018 or BAPE x Coach 2020 are considered important milestones that help mark the popularity and position of streetwear in the fashion world.
2. Let's admire a series of cool streetwear combinations
Wide t-shirt mixed with skirt

It seems like it has nothing to do with mixing a loose t-shirt with a skirt and a pair of bold black boots to help you get a very personal outfit. The way to change the set of clothes is not only harmonious but also highly applicable.
Combine a black oversized t-shirt with loose checkered pants

The combination style is receiving a lot of response from the street style community. In addition, girls can mix it with straight skirts, A-line skirts or pleated skirts to make them more adorable and attractive.
